cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category as it proposes a new gated unit for Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs). It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category as it discusses finding the best practices for RNNs. Additionally, it could be categorized under Computation and Language (cs.CL) as it deals with sequence data. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) are also possible categories as RNNs are commonly used in these fields.
